improvement ideas:
1) paralelize samples processing (with &)
2) make separate module for each step of the tool
3) do Tophat mapping outside the tool
4) make parameter flexible with default values
5) make output organization better, ex. logs folder
6) fill-in form for input parameters (species, adapter, files, ...)

observations:
1) implemented for single-end sequencing data, not tested for paired-end
2) TopHat2 is run without gtf file, to prevent problemes caused by different chromosomes notation in gtf and index files
3) both bowtie and bowtie 2 indexes are needed
4) a reference directory is needed containing genome.fa, genome_ref.txt, genome.gtf, mature_ref.fa, other_ref.fa, hairpin_ref.fa, bowtie and bowtie2 indexes of genome.fa
5) miRNA counts used are not the normalized ones, but the raw ones

